    "days_left": 28,
    "rationale": "Multi-channel from zero: Facebook (posts/Reels/$7-day ads) + YouTube Shorts + SEO/AEO blog, all soft-funneling to Consent Resolve. First 14 days are warm-up, so audience numbers are back-loaded to weeks 3-4. Targets weight LEADING indicators I directly control (videos shipped, posts, ad views) over lagging outcomes (followers, subs). Video is the engine on both FB and YouTube; the 'Angi/pricing/leads' content does double duty as Shorts, Reels, and AI-citable blog posts. Benchmarks: ~150-250 FB followers and a small-but-real YouTube base are realistic for month 1 from zero with this budget. Recalibrated weekly against actuals.",
